name: NEVPNIKEv2SecurityAssociationParameters
desc: NEVPNIKEv2SecurityAssociationParameters contains parameters for an IKEv2 Security Association.

items.name: var encryptionAlgorithm: NEVPNIKEv2EncryptionAlgorithm
items.desc: The algorithm used by the Security Association to encrypt and decrypt data.

items.name: var integrityAlgorithm: NEVPNIKEv2IntegrityAlgorithm
items.desc: The algorithm used by the Security Association to verify the integrity of data.

items.name: var diffieHellmanGroup: NEVPNIKEv2DiffieHellmanGroup
items.desc: The Diffie Hellman group used by the Security Association.

items.name: var lifetimeMinutes: Int32
items.desc: The duration of the lifetime of the Security Association, in minutes.
